rComments: Pretty easy class, just really boring. The lecture drags and I've never watched so many youtube videos before in my life. She puts the lecture slides online. No reading necessary. As long as you memorize the notes and put in the minimum effort required, you should get at an A.

She's kind of boring, but all the random world music will keep you awake during lecture. If you can also manage to pay attention during lecture she pretty much gives you all the answers for the tests. There is just a lot of annoying unnecessary memorization of instrument names and junk. Overall a pretty annoying class, but not too bad.
